\b\fs28 Sending Commands
\b0\fs24 \
You can easily send manual commands to the MAKE Controller Kit over Ethernet or USB, using OSC messages (check the OSC tutorial online, accessible via the 
\b Help
\b0  menu item).  Sending manual OSC messages is great for quickly checking if your board is doing what you think it should be doing, using nothing more than an Ethernet or USB cable.\
